doc.after: Arising from the merger with Pulkovo Airlines the bulk of the scheduled service operation is from Russia s second largest city St Petersburg where Pulkovo was the dominant airline and Rossiya continues to be Operations based in Moscow are predominantly non scheduled ones for state organisations or flights operated on behalf of Aeroflot Rossiya continues Pulkovo s lead role on the Moscow St Petersburg route
